				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$${n \mathord{\left/ {\vphantom {n {v_{F} }}} \right. \kern-\nulldelimiterspace} {v_{F} }}$$\end{document} ratio of M2GaC MAX phases is in order of n/vFHf2GaC>n/vFZr2GaC\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
